item.title: Visibility and Profiling in Django (Python3)
item.description: The ‘batteries included’ python framework will required a few tools to get insights into the application performance and other metrics. This article is by no means exhaustive. But, it serves as a good start and simplifies geting started. ncalls is the total number of calls that the function makes. tottime is the total time spent in the function alone. cumtime is the total time spent in the function plus all the functions that it in-turn calls.
